{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775863360983,"sessionID":"ses_2864be159ffehrySNsT9JNg1Wc","part":{"id":"prt_d79b46737001QXVe2HZmW36vD7","messageID":"msg_d79b45004001P8jDUSxfsPrGip","sessionID":"ses_2864be159ffehrySNsT9JNg1Wc","type":"tool","tool":"grep","callID":"toolu_c8ccad7dbd224ca2afc5eb0b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"pattern":"AR-018|idle.*cleanup|空闲清理","path":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z","include":"*.md"},"output":"Found 53 matches\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-018/tasks.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-018 — Agentd Idle Cleanup Controller Tasks\n  Line 7: | AR | AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 |\n  Line 107: ### Phase 5: IdleCleanupController Implementation (`idle_cleanup.go`)\n  Line 109: - [ ] **TASK-040**: Define `CleanupResult` struct in `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup.go`\n  Line 112: - [ ] **TASK-041**: Define `IdleCleanupController` interface in `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup.go`\n  Line 115: - [ ] **TASK-042**: Define `idleCleanupController` struct in `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup.go`\n  Line 118: - [ ] **TASK-043**: Implement `NewIdleCleanupController(config *CleanupConfig, agentClient versioned.Interface, idleTracker IdleTracker, metrics *CleanupMetrics, logger klog.Logger) IdleCleanupController` in `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup.go`\n  Line 120: - [ ] **TASK-044**: Implement `Start(ctx context.Context) error` method in `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup.go`\n  Line 126: - [ ] **TASK-045**: Implement `Stop()` method in `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup.go`\n  Line 131: - [ ] **TASK-046**: Implement `CleanupNow(ctx context.Context) (CleanupResult, error)` method in `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup.go`\n  Line 135: - [ ] **TASK-047**: Implement `runCleanup(ctx context.Context)` method in `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup.go`\n  Line 137:   - List idle AgentRuntimes and submit cleanup tasks\n  Line 138:   - List idle CodeInterpreters and submit cleanup tasks\n  Line 141: - [ ] **TASK-048**: Implement `cleanupResource(ctx context.Context, kind, namespace, name string) error` method in `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup.go`\n  Line 149: - [ ] **TASK-049**: Implement `isNamespaceAllowed(namespace string) bool` method in `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup.go`\n  Line 153: ### Phase 6: Resource Watching (`idle_cleanup.go`)\n  Line 155: - [ ] **TASK-050**: Implement `watchResources(ctx context.Context)` method in `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup.go`\n  Line 160: - [ ] **TASK-051**: Implement `watchAgentRuntimes(ctx context.Context)` method in `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup.go`\n  Line 166: - [ ] **TASK-052**: Implement `watchCodeInterpreters(ctx context.Context)` method in `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup.go`\n  Line 169: - [ ] **TASK-053**: Implement `updateResourceActivity(key ResourceKey, lastActivity, creation metav1.Time)` method in `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup.go`\n  Line 251: - [ ] **TEST-040**: Create `TestIdleCleanupController_Start_Disabled` in `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup_test.go`\n  Line 255: - [ ] **TEST-041**: Create `TestIdleCleanupController_Stop` in `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup_test.go`\n  Line 259: - [ ] **TEST-042**: Create `TestIdleCleanupController_runCleanup` in `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup_test.go`\n  Line 264: - [ ] **TEST-043**: Create `TestIdleCleanupController_cleanupResource_DryRun` in `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup_test.go`\n  Line 268: - [ ] **TEST-044**: Create `TestIdleCleanupController_cleanupResource_NotFound` in `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup_test.go`\n  Line 272: - [ ] **TEST-045**: Create `TestIdleCleanupController_isNamespaceAllowed` in `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup_test.go`\n  Line 277: - [ ] **TEST-046**: Create `TestIdleCleanupController_CleanupNow` in `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup_test.go`\n  Line 319: - [ ] **DOC-001**: Add Go doc comments to all public types in `config.go`, `errors.go`, `idle_tracker.go`, `cleanup_metrics.go`, `idle_cleanup.go`\n  Line 330:   - Document idle cleanup controller\n  Line 397:   - Verify config.go, errors.go, idle_tracker.go, cleanup_metrics.