n last-activity timestamps in the store for idle cleanup\n  Line 78: - Agentd idle cleanup controller (separate controller component)\n  Line 172: - Harder to implement idle cleanup\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-008/VERIFICATION_REPORT.md:\n  Line 114: **Test Coverage**: 8 passing tests covering construction, lifecycle, idle cleanup, expired cleanup, error handling, and timeout scenarios.\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/sandbox-orchestration/AR-006-sandbox-deletion-lifecycle/tasks.md:\n  Line 258: - [ ] GarbageCollector implemented with idle and expired cleanup\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/idle-cleanup/design.md:\n  Line 118: - `LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"` — **read by agentd** for idle cleanup.\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/project.md:\n  Line 10: session-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\n  Line 35:   Agentd (idle cleanup controller)","metadata":{"matches":53,"truncated":false},"title":"AR-018|idle.*cleanup|空闲清理","time":{"start":1775863360962,"end":1775863360981}}}}
