{"type":"text","timestamp":1775863466977,"sessionID":"ses_2864be159ffehrySNsT9JNg1Wc","part":{"id":"prt_d79b587140014kZQzqMdea30iQ","messageID":"msg_d79b57df1001oVuulbaPa5l87J","sessionID":"ses_2864be159ffehrySNsT9JNg1Wc","type":"text","text":"Now let me compile the verification report. Based on my analysis:\n\n## AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 Verification Report\n\n### Executive Summary\n\n**Status**: ❌ **NOT COMPLIANT** - Critical implementation gaps identified\n\nThe current workspace (`qwen3.5-plus`) does **not** have the client-go infrastructure or idle cleanup controller implementation required by the spec. The AR-018 tasks are defined but not implemented.\n\n---\n\n### Detailed Analysis\n\n#### 1. Client-Go Library Spec Compliance (`deployment/client-go.md`)\n\n**Required Structure:**\n```\nclient-go/\n├── clientset/versioned/\n│   ├── clientset.go (Interface, Clientset)\n│   ├── scheme/\n│   ├── typed/runtime/v1alpha1/\n│   │   ├── runtime_client.go (RuntimeV1alpha1Interface)\n│   │   ├── agentruntime.go (AgentRuntimeInterface)\n│   │   └── codeinterpreter.go (CodeInterpreterInterface)\n│   └── fake/\n├── informers/externalversions/\n└── listers/runtime/v1alpha1/\n```\n\n**Current Status**: ❌ **NOT IMPLEMENTED**\n\n- No `client-go/` directory exists in the current workspace\n- No generated typed clients (`AgentRuntimeInterface`, `CodeInterpreterInterface`)\n- No informer factories or listers\n- Reference implementation exists in `MiniMax-M2.5` workspace but not integrated\n\n**Comparison with Reference Implementation** (`MiniMax-M2.5` workspace):\n\n| Component | Spec Requirement | Reference Implementation | Compliant |\n|-----------|-----------------|-------------------------|-----------|\n| `Clientset.Interface` | `Discovery()`, `RuntimeV1alpha1()` | Only `RuntimeV1alpha1()` | ⚠️ Partial |\n| `NewForConfig` | ✅ Required | ✅ Implemented | ✅ Yes |\n| `NewForConfigOrDie` | ✅ Required | ✅ Implemented | ✅ Yes |\n| `New(c rest.Interface)` | ✅ Required | ❌ Different signature | ❌ No |\n| `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` | `RESTClient()`, `AgentRuntimesGetter`, `CodeInterpretersGetter` | ✅ Implemented | ✅ Yes |\n| `AgentRuntimeInterface` | 9 methods + expansion | ✅ All 9 methods | ✅ Yes |\n| `CodeInterpreterInterface` | 9 methods + expansion | ✅ All 9 methods | ✅ Yes |\n| REST plural `agentruntimes` | ✅ Required | ✅ Used | ✅ Yes |\n| REST plural `codeinterpreters` | ✅ Required | ✅ Used | ✅ Yes |\n\n**Gaps in Reference Implementation**:\n1. Missing `Discovery()` method in `Clientset.Interface`\n2. Missing `NewForConfigAndClient()` constructor\n3. Missing `discovery.DiscoveryClient` embedding\n4. Missing scheme/package-level `ParameterCodec` export\n5. Missing informer factory (`SharedInformerFactory`)\n6. Missing lister interfaces (`AgentRuntimeLister`)\n7. Missing expansion interfaces\n\n---\n\n#### 2. AR-018 Idle Cleanup Controller Implementation\n\n**Required Files** (per `changes/AR-018/tasks.md`):\n- `pkg/agentd/config.go` - CleanupConfig structure\n- `pkg/agentd/errors.go` - CleanupError types\n- `pkg/agentd/idle_tracker.go` - IdleTracker interface/implementation\n- `pkg/agentd/cleanup_metrics.go` - CleanupMetrics\n- `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup.go` - IdleCleanupController\n- `pkg/agentd/*_test.go` - Unit tests\n\n**Current Status**: ❌ **NOT IMPLEMENTED**\n\n**Existing Files in `pkg/agentd/`**:\n| File | Purpose | Status |\n|------|---------|--------|\n| `constants.go` | Timeout constants | ⚠️ Only has sandbox-related constants |\n| `controller.go` | Reconciler for Sandbox | ❌ Wrong type (uses custom Sandbox, not AgentRuntime) |\n| `controller_test.go` | Controller tests | ❌ Tests wrong controller |\n\n**Missing Files**:\n- ❌ `config.go` - No cleanup configuration\n- ❌ `errors.go` - No cleanup error types\n- ❌ `idle_tracker.go` - No idle state tracking\n- ❌ `cleanup_metrics.go` - No metrics\n- ❌ `idle_cleanup.go` - No idle cleanup controller\n- ❌ `config_test.go`, `errors_test.go`, `idle_tracker_test.go`, `idle_cleanup_test.go`\n\n---\n\n#### 3. API Contract Verification\n\n**Spec Interface Requirements**:\n\n```go\n// AgentRuntimeInterface - ALL methods missing\ntype AgentRuntimeInterface interface {\n    Create(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    Update(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n    DeleteCollection(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.DeleteOptions, listOpts metav1.ListOptions) error\n    Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList, error)\n    Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n    Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    AgentRuntimeExpansion\n}\n```\n\n**Current Implementation**: ❌ **Interface does not exist**\n\nThe controller uses `controller-runtime` client instead of typed client:\n```go\ntype Reconciler struct {\n    client.Client  // controller-runtime client, not typed\n    Scheme *runtime.Scheme\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n#### 4. Test Coverage\n\n**Required Tests** (per `changes/AR-018/tasks.md`):\n- Config tests: `TestDefaultCleanupConfig`, `TestLoadCleanupConfigFromEnv_*`, `TestCleanupConfig_Validate`\n- Error tests: `TestCleanupError_Error`\n- IdleTracker tests: `TestIdleTracker_UpdateLastActivity`, `TestIdleTracker_IsIdle`, etc.\n- Metrics tests: `TestCleanupMetrics_RecordCleanup`\n- Controller tests: `TestIdleCleanupController_Start_Disabled`, `TestIdleC